{"tid":1105913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"江西3歲女童玩耍跌倒　手中筷子從口直插入顱內10厘米","createTime":"2019-04-14T08:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T18:31:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f8424db10e298408e3ff9cc35509df1890038eee","tid":1105913,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"4月11日（上周四），江西萍鄉一名3歲女童吃飯時手持筷子在客廳奔跑玩耍，不慎跌倒，導致一根25厘米長的筷子有10厘米從口腔插入顱內。幸運的是筷子沒有刺破重要組織，醫生連夜為女童進行手術，順利取出筷子<br />\n報道指，女童被送至中南大學湘雅醫院時哭鬧不止，只見一根筷子從右上至左下經扁桃體上極斜插入咽部，甚至頸左側後部可觸摸到筷子尖，但女童口腔內沒有明顯出血。電腦斷層掃描（CT）顯示，筷子插入女童顱內長達10 厘米，但未傷及腦幹、頸動脈和頸椎等重要組織。<br />\n該院耳鼻咽喉科的黃東海副教授表示，「筷子避開了所有的重要組織，僅僅是刺傷了軟組織，這是不幸中的萬幸」。但是女童情緒躁動，使得筷子隨時可能偏倚而導致病情變化，必須要及時取出筷子。該院醫生隨即為女童開展會診評估及進行手術，並順利取出筷子。<br />\n（《瀟湘晨報》）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2676062/org/25073fb86c9fd24a498abc43243aa7c0.png/VRrrCQpFFST6nQcRQepo7inEBEfkhr6QJGqhXCRqoVw?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2676062%2Forg%2F25073fb86c9fd24a498abc43243aa7c0.png%2FVRrrCQpFFST6nQcRQepo7inEBEfkhr6QJGqhXCRqoVw%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a0e0a44c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2676060/org/0d96d85aba76d167341d68d360669016.jpg/QxUdUxjeZP4ytotSXHv7WcL7KELB7gYl6rwp9eq8KfU?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2676060%2Forg%2F0d96d85aba76d167341d68d360669016.jpg%2FQxUdUxjeZP4ytotSXHv7WcL7KELB7gYl6rwp9eq8KfU%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=8929c8fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/317841/%E6%B1%9F%E8%A5%BF3%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E7%8E%A9%E8%80%8D%E8%B7%8C%E5%80%92-%E6%89%8B%E4%B8%AD%E7%AD%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%BE%9E%E5%8F%A3%E7%9B%B4%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E9%A1%B1%E5%85%A710%E5%8E%98%E7%B1%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F317841%2F%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8